description: Stunningly renovated One Bedroom/One bathroom condo in Midtown. Features include beautiful bamboo floor, fresh paint, new granite counter top and backsplash, new AC. Kitchen includes hardwood cabinetry accented with stainless steel appliances. Lease includes one assigned parking space, laundry units and high speed internet. Tenant pay electricity and water/sewer utilities. Mayfair Tower is one of Midtown's best iconic place to live and is conveniently located in the heart of Midtown just steps to Piedmont Park, Woodruff Arts Center and Atlanta Symphony, High Museum, Colony Square, and various dinning and entertainment options. In addition Mayfair Tower amenities include Guest Parking, Fitness Center, On-Site Dog Park, On Site Car Wash. English Garden and Additional New Grill Lounge.
